                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for preparing lignin, alkali liquor, pentose, hydrogen and oxygen from black liquor generated in paper pulp production by electrodialysis method",
                    "一种用电渗析法从生产纸浆产生的黑液中制取木质素、碱液、五碳糖、氢气和氧气的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the technical field of deep development and high-value utilization of biomass waste resources, and discloses a method for preparing lignin, alkali liquor, pentose, hydrogen and oxygen from black liquor generated in paper pulp production by using an electrodialysis method. The method comprises the following steps: feeding black liquor into a mother liquor chamber of an electrodialysis device, feeding water into an alkali liquor chamber of the electrodialysis device, and carrying out electrodialysis reaction to obtain lignin suspension, alkali liquor, hydrogen and oxygen; mixing the lignin suspension and a flocculating agent, and filtering to obtain lignin and pentose filtrate; the black liquor is black liquor generated in paper pulp production; lignin suspension and oxygen are generated by the mother liquor chamber; the lye and hydrogen are generated by the lye chamber. The method provided by the invention has the advantages of low equipment investment, low treatment cost, low equipment energy consumption, long service life and small occupied area, can simultaneously obtain five products, and does not generate secondary pollution. Meanwhile, high-value utilization of all components (cellulose, lignin and hemicellulose) of biomass resources is achieved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于生物质废弃资源的深度开发和高值利用技术领域，本发明公开了一种用电渗析法从生产纸浆产生的黑液中制取木质素、碱液、五碳糖、氢气和氧气的方法。所述方法包括如下步骤：将黑液送入电渗析装置的母液室，将水送入电渗析装置的碱液室，进行电渗析反应，得到木质素悬浮液、碱液、氢气和氧气；木质素悬浮液和絮凝剂混合后过滤，得到木质素和五碳糖滤液；黑液为生产纸浆产生的黑液；木质素悬浮液和氧气由母液室产生；碱液和氢气由碱液室产生。本发明所述方法，设备投资少、处理费用低、设备能耗低、使用寿命长、占地面积小，能同时得到5种产物，不产生二次污染。同时做到了生物质资源的全组分(纤维素、木质素、半纤维素)高值化利用。"
                }
            ]
